org.lobobrowser.html.w3c

Interface HTMLTableCellElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, HTMLElement, Node
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HTMLTableDataCellElement, HTMLTableHeaderCellElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HTMLTableCellElementImpl, HTMLTableHeadElementImpl

    public interface HTMLTableCellElement
extends HTMLElement
    The object used to represent the TH and TD elements. See the TD element definition in HTML 4.01.

    See also the Object Model (DOM) Level 2 HTML Specification

    .
